@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: User Logs In

actor User
participant "Frontend/UI" as UI
participant "Backend/API" as API
database "Database" as DB

User -> UI: Open 'Login' page
User -> UI: Fill login form\nand submit
UI -> API: POST /login (credentials)
API -> DB: Verify user credentials
DB --> API: Success/Failure response
API --> UI: Return result (success/failure)
UI --> User: Show confirmation or error

@enduml
